<h2 class="wp-block-heading">FAQ</h2>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">H√§ufige Fragen zum Thema Designstrategie</h3>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<div class="schema-faq wp-block-yoast-faq-block">
<div class="schema-faq-section" id="faq-question-1718092026677"><strong class="schema-faq-question">Was¬†ist eine Designstrategie?</strong> </p>
